    "id": "anti_centered_subject_default",
    "category": "composition",
    "name_zh": "反例：默认居中",
    "summary": "新手拍人下意识把脸放正中央；除非对称构图，否则居中=单调",
    "axes": ["composition", "subject_fit"],
    "scene_modes": ["portrait", "documentary"],
    "person_count_range": [1, 4],
    "priority": 5,
    "when_to_use": ["新手避雷"],
    "evidence": "三分构图存在的根本原因就是因为人眼不喜欢正中；居中只是『没找到位置』",
    "watch_out": "对称水面 / 对称建筑 / 双胞胎合影 = 居中合理；其他不要默认",
    "counter_example": "对称是反例的反例",
    "tags": ["反例", "居中", "新手"],
    "citations": [
      { "source": "Bryan Peterson《Learning to See Creatively》", "chapter": "Avoid Center" }
